<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="relax-v">relax <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'læks/    美 /rɪ'læks/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(使) 放松：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Enjoying art and music is also a good way to relax.
欣赏美术和音乐也是放松的好方法。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We get so much homework that I don’t have free time to relax. 
我们有很多作业要做，没有空闲时间放松。</p><footer>北师大⑤ – 14</footer></div>

